title: Ep. 371 - Does Anyone Really Care About Impeachment?
description:
The impeachment saga doesn't seem to be resonating with the public the way Clinton's impeachment did. Why is that? Also, a millionaire pop star is threatening a charity organization because it isn't ideologically pure enough for her tastes. And the persecution of undercover journalist David Daleiden continues. Why isn't conservative media paying much attention to it? Date: 11-14-2019
